            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="porn as a video game??"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>porn as a video game??<span> (0)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><span class="author" title="author name and user ID">Anonymous Coward</span> | about 3 years ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2274044&cid=36585682">(#36585682)</a></h4>
